    "html": "<div style=\"position:relative;width:100%;height:100%;background:var(--surface-dark);background-color:var(--surface-dark);overflow:hidden;\">\n            <div style=\"background: var(--texture-grain); inset: 0; opacity: 0.04; z-index: 1; position: absolute; pointer-events: none\"></div>\n            \n            <div class=\"slide-content\" style=\"position:relative;z-index:10;padding:80px var(--space-6) 80px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center;height:100%;width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;overflow:hidden;\">\n                <div style=\"width:100%;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:12px;\"><h2 style=\"font-family: Playfair Display; font-size: 25px; font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.12; color: #EDEEF5; margin: 0 0 12px; text-align: left; letter-spacing: -0.015em; overflow-wrap: break-word\">Three Modes of Transmission</h2><div style=\"display:flex;gap:12px;width:100%;\"><div style=\"flex:1;min-width:0;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.05);border:1px solid #2A2C3D;border-top:3px solid #767CFF;border-radius:0;padding:16px 14px 14px;box-sizing:border-box;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:space-between;gap:8px;\">\n                <div>\n                    <div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;margin-bottom:6px;\">\n                        <span style=\"font-family:Playfair Display;font-size:10px;font-weight:900;color:#767CFF;background:#767CFF18;padding:2px 6px;border-radius:4px;\">01 PILLAR</span>\n                    </div>\n                    <h3 style=\"font-family:Playfair Display;font-size:14px;font-weight:900;color:#EDEEF5;margin:0 0 6px;line-height:1.2;\">Spoken</h3>\n                    <p style=\"font-family:DM Sans;font-size:11px;color:#CBCDD8;line-height:1.45;margin:0;\">Words carry intention. The teacher&#x27;s voice shapes how wisdom lands \u2014 not just what is said, but how it is offered.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div style=\"font-family:Playfair Display;font-size:9.5px;font-weight:800;color:#767CFF;background:#767CFF15;padding:3px 8px;border-radius:999px;width:fit-content;\">\u26a1 High Speed</div>\n            </div><div style=\"flex:1;min-width:0;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.05);border:1px solid #2A2C3D;border-top:3px solid #767CFF;border-radius:0;padding:16px 14px 14px;box-sizing:border-box;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:space-between;gap:8px;\">\n                <div>\n                    <div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;margin-bottom:6px;\">\n                        <span style=\"font-family:Playfair Display;font-size:10px;font-weight:900;color:#767CFF;background:#767CFF18;padding:2px 6px;border-radius:4px;\">02 PILLAR</span>\n                    </div>\n                    <h3 style=\"font-family:Playfair Display;font-size:14px;font-weight:900;color:#EDEEF5;margin:0 0 6px;line-height:1.2;\">Written</h3>\n                    <p style=\"font-family:DM Sans;font-size:11px;color:#CBCDD8;line-height:1.45;margin:0;\">Text endures. Written wisdom survives the session, the teacher, and the era. It becomes a reference the student returns to.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div style=\"font-family:Playfair Display;font-size:9.5px;font-weight:800;color:#767CFF;background:#767CFF15;padding:3px 8px;border-radius:999px;width:fit-content;\">\ud83d\udee1\ufe0f 100% Precision</div>\n            </div><div style=\"flex:1;min-width:0;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.05);border:1px solid #2A2C3D;border-top:3px solid #767CFF;border-radius:0;padding:16px 14px 14px;box-sizing:border-box;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:space-between;gap:8px;\">\n                <div>\n                    <div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;margin-bottom:6px;\">\n                        <span style=\"font-family:Playfair Display;font-size:10px;font-weight:900;color:#767CFF;background:#767CFF18;padding:2px 6px;border-radius:4px;\">03 PILLAR</span>\n                    </div>\n                    <h3 style=\"font-family:Playfair Display;font-size:14px;font-weight:900;color:#EDEEF5;margin:0 0 6px;line-height:1.2;\">Lived</h3>\n                    <p style=\"font-family:DM Sans;font-size:11px;color:#CBCDD8;line-height:1.45;margin:0;\">The deepest teaching is embodied. When the teacher lives what they teach, every interaction becomes a transmission.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div style=\"font-family:Playfair Display;font-size:9.5px;font-weight:800;color:#767CFF;background:#767CFF15;padding:3px 8px;border-radius:999px;width:fit-content;\">\ud83d\udee1\ufe0f 100% Precision</div>\n            </div></div></div>\n            </div>\n        </div>",
